                <target><![CDATA[  <ul>
                           	<li><a class="link-underlined " href="#filter">Filter Pages</a></li>
                           	<li><a class="link-underlined" href="#add">Add new Page</a></li>
                           	<li><a class="link-underlined" href="#List">List of Pages&nbsp;</a></li>
                           </ul>

                           <h2><a id="filter" name="filter"></a>Filter Pages</h2>

                           <p>The Pages can be filtert by several Parameter.<br />
                           Language and Name is the default and&nbsp;always shown. If more options are required, the filter can be expanded by clicking on &quot;More filter options&quot;.</p>

                           <p><img alt="Filter" src="/bundles/networkinginitcms/images/helptext/pages/pages_list_filter.png" style="width: 600px; height: 102px;" /></p>

                           <p>if more then one option is entered, just Pages, fitting ALL the criteria are shown.&nbsp;</p>

                           <h2><a id="add" name="add"></a>Add new Page</h2>

                           <p>To add a new Page, just click the Add Page Button</p>

                           <p><img alt="" src="/bundles/networkinginitcms/images/helptext/pages/pages_list_add.png" style="line-height: 1.6em; width: 93px; height: 39px;" /></p>

                           <p>Please go to the <a class="link-underlined " href="/admin/help/networking_init_cms.page.admin.page/create">Create Page Help Text</a> to find more information</p>

                           <h2><a id="List" name="List"></a>List of Pages</h2>

                           <p><img alt="" src="/bundles/networkinginitcms/images/helptext/pages/pages_list.png" style="width: 600px; height: 202px;" /></p>

                           <p>By clicking on the pen icon, the pages can be <a class="link-underlined" href="/admin/help/networking_init_cms.page.admin.page/edit">edited</a>.&nbsp;<br />
                           &nbsp;</p> ]]></target>
            </trans-unit>

            <trans-unit id="networking_init_cms.page.admin.page.create.title">
                <source>networking_init_cms.page.admin.page.create.title</source>
