            <trans-unit id="networking_init_cms.page.admin.page.edit.text">
                <source>networking_init_cms.page.admin.page.edit.text</source>
                <target><![CDATA[    <p>The Edit Form has multiple areas</p>

                           <ul>
                           	<li><a class="link-underlined" href="#status">Publishing Status</a></li>
                           	<li><a class="link-underlined" href="#content">Content</a></li>
                           	<li><a class="link-underlined" href="#translations">Translations</a></li>
                           	<li><a class="link-underlined" href="#menu">Menu Connections</a></li>
                           	<li><a class="link-underlined" href="#setting">Settings &amp; SEO</a></li>
                           </ul>

                           <p><a id="status" name="status"></a><strong>Publishing Status</strong></p>

                           <p>A page can have 3 different status.&nbsp;</p>

                           <ol>
                           	<li><strong>Draft</strong><br />
                           	As soon something on the page is edited, the status is changed to &quot;draft&quot;. The changes are not visible on the frontend. if all the changes are made, the status should be changed to review or publish<br />
                           	if necessary, all changes can be discard.</li>
                           	<li><strong>Review</strong><br />
                           	someone has made changes to the page. Before the are put online, the changes should be reviewed.&nbsp;</li>
                           	<li><strong>Published</strong>&nbsp;<br />
                           	if all the changes are correct, the status can be changed to publish. the site is not online.</li>
                           </ol>

                           <p><a id="content" name="content"></a><strong>Content</strong></p>

                           <p>In the content, the different areas ot the page are displayed (e.g. left column). for each area, multiple blocks can be assigend. those blocks can be either text or galleries. new blocks can be created by clicking on the + icon. existing blocks can be deleted or edited by clicking on the accoring icon.&nbsp;</p>

                           <p><a id="translations" name="translations"></a><strong>Translations</strong></p>

                           <p>If this page exists in another language, a link to this page can be createt. as alternative option, the page can be copied to another language.</p>

                           <p><a id="menu" name="menu"></a><strong>Menu Connections</strong></p>

                           <p>all menu connections can be handelt here.</p>

                           <p><a id="setting" name="setting"></a><strong>Settings &amp; SEO</strong></p>

                           <p>the settings descript in the &quot;<a href="/admin/help/networking_init_cms.page.admin.page/create" title="link-underlined">create page</a>&quot; can be changed by clicking on the pen icon.&nbsp;</p>
                             ]]></target>
            </trans-unit>

